  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5620888/" class="title-link">听说太理想的一切都不可接触，我再置身寂寞路途...</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5620888"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/redwing/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1032503-217.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/redwing/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">温情小颖颖</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-10-18"
      class="main-meta">2012-10-18 04:29:05</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5620888_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  亲爱的表哥： 遥知你近日在京诸事不顺，具体原因无非还是人际关系紧张以及对世俗世界的不能理解。适逢我近日又相对闭关地把这书看完，虽然这书和你近来的忧心事没有绝对的联系，但是人际关系紧张、对世俗世界理解不能、自我定位模糊等等——这些共同的内心痛苦，一直是我们之间...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5620888/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
